---
// src/pages/projects/project-3.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Siege X Guide" backgroundColor="#412E20">
  <main class="project-detail-container">
    <article class="project-detail" transition:name="project-3">
      <a href="/projects" class="back-link">
        <span class="arrow">←</span>
        <span>back to projects</span>
      </a>
      <div class="project-header">
        <h1>Siege X Guide</h1>
        <span class="tag">Next.js</span>
      </div>
      
      <p class="project-intro">
        Interactive Rainbow Six Siege tactical guide featuring comprehensive map callouts, operator strategies, and gameplay tips for competitive players.
      </p>

      <div class="project-content">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
          Siege X Guide is a modern web application designed to help Rainbow Six Siege players improve their tactical gameplay. The app provides detailed interactive maps, operator guides, and strategic information for 15+ competitive maps. Built with Next.js 15 and featuring smooth animations with Framer Motion, it offers an intuitive interface for accessing over 200 strategies across 60+ operators.
        </p>

        <h2>Technologies Used</h2>
        <div class="project-tech">
          <span>Next.js 15</span>
          <span>React 19</span>
          <span>TypeScript</span>
          <span>Tailwind CSS 4</span>
          <span>Framer Motion</span>
          <span>Zustand</span>
          <span>Radix UI</span>
          <span>Vercel</span>
        </div>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Interactive map viewer with 15+ Rainbow Six Siege competitive maps</li>
          <li>Comprehensive operator guides covering 60+ operators</li>
          <li>200+ tactical strategies including callouts and lineups</li>
          <li>Smooth animations and transitions with Framer Motion</li>
          <li>State management with Zustand for optimal performance</li>
          <li>Accessible UI components built with Radix UI primitives</li>
          <li>Responsive design optimized for desktop and mobile gameplay reference</li>
          <li>Analytics integration for usage insights</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Technical Highlights</h2>
        <p>
          The application leverages Next.js 15's latest features including the App Router for optimal performance and SEO. State management is handled efficiently with Zustand, providing a lightweight alternative to Redux while maintaining excellent developer experience. The UI is built with Radix UI components for accessibility compliance, styled with Tailwind CSS 4 for rapid development, and enhanced with Framer Motion for fluid animations that don't compromise performance.
        </p>

        <h2>Challenges & Solutions</h2>
        <p>
          One of the main challenges was managing the large amount of tactical data while maintaining fast load times and smooth interactions. This was solved by implementing efficient state management with Zustand, lazy loading map images, and using Next.js's image optimization. The interactive map viewer required careful consideration of touch and mouse events to work seamlessly across devices, which was achieved through custom event handlers and Framer Motion's gesture recognition.
        </p>

        <div class="project-links">
          <a href="https://siege-x-guide.vercel.app/" 
             class="project-link-btn primary"
             target="_blank"
             rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <span>Live Demo</span>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/snezzz0/siegexguide" 
             class="project-link-btn"
             target="_blank"
             rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <span>View Code</span>
            <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>

  .project-detail-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .back-link {
    position: absolute;
    top: -3rem;
    left: 0;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #FFE4AF;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', 'FiraCode Nerd Font', monospace;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    z-index: 10;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #EC753A;
  }

  .arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-detail {
    background: #412E20;
    border: 3px solid #DA9F5F;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .project-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .project-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #FFE4AF;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tag {
    background: #DA9F5F;
    color: #342331;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid #EC753A;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .project-intro {
    color: #DA9F5F;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-content h2 {
    color: #FFE4AF;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .project-content p {
    color: #DA9F5F;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-tech {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .project-tech span {
    background: rgba(218, 159, 95, 0.2);
    color: #DA9F5F;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid #DA9F5F;
  }

  .project-content ul {
    color: #DA9F5F;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .project-link-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: #EC753A;
    border: 2px solid #EC753A;
    padding: 1rem 1.75rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: 'Fira Code', 'FiraCode Nerd Font', monospace;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .project-link-btn.primary {
    background: #EC753A;
    color: #342331;
  }

  .project-link-btn:hover {
    background: #EC753A;
    color: #342331;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(236, 117, 58, 0.3);
  }

  .project-link-btn.primary:hover {
    background: #DA9F5F;
    border-color: #DA9F5F;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-detail-container {
      padding: 3rem 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      top: -2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .project-detail {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .project-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .project-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .project-links {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .project-link-btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
